== Main screen (main.dart) — unfixed issues from Audit Phase 1 ==

1. _showPhotoGallery uses wrong item ID for photo removal
   File: main.dart, _showPhotoGallery() ~line 1066
   Problem: When all photos are missing and user confirms "Remove reference",
   the code uses _selectedItemId to clear the photo field. But _selectedItemId
   is set by onTap on ListTile, while photo icon is a separate IconButton in
   trailing. User can tap photo icon without selecting that ListTile first,
   so _selectedItemId may point to a different item.
   Fix: Pass itemId as parameter to _showPhotoGallery() instead of relying on _selectedItemId.

2. Context menu position is hardcoded
   File: main.dart, _showContextMenu() ~line 2029
   Problem: showMenu position is RelativeRect.fromLTRB(200, 200, 200, 200) — always
   appears at same screen position regardless of which item was long-pressed.
   Fix: Use the tap position or item widget position to place the menu near the item.

3. Error widget has hardcoded English string
   File: main.dart, _buildErrorWidget() ~line 2822
   Problem: 'Error loading image:\n$error' — not wrapped in lw().
   Fix: Use lw('Error loading image') + ':\n$error'

4. Filter status shows (F) inside virtual folders
   File: main.dart, getFilterStatusText() ~line 258
   Problem: When user enters a virtual folder (Yearly, Daily, etc.), xvFilter is set
   to e.g. 'yearly:true', so getFilterStatusText() returns '(F)' which is misleading.
   Fix: Either suppress filter indicator inside virtual folders, or show folder-specific text.

== Add/Edit screen (additem.dart) — unfixed issues from Audit Phase 1 ==

5. _checkTimeConflict doesn't check weekday overlap for daily reminders
   File: additem.dart, _checkTimeConflict() ~line 1401
   Problem: When checking cross-item time conflicts for daily reminders, it only checks
   if the time string matches but doesn't compare daily_days bitmasks. Two daily reminders
   at 09:00 on Mon/Wed and Tue/Thu would trigger a false conflict warning.
   Fix: Compare daily_days bitmasks — only warn if (daysA & daysB) != 0.
   Severity: Low — it's just a warning, doesn't block save.

== Settings screen (settings.dart) — unfixed issues from Audit Phase 1 ==

6. FIXED: "Debug logs" toggle fully works — saved to DB, read on startup, updates xvDebug at runtime

7. FIXED: "Enable daily reminders" toggle now cancels/reschedules daily reminders
